room_title: Escape room "Hotel’s Secrets" by Escape Zone Houston in Houston
room_description:
Book now with the promo code  WOE  and get a 20% discount!

There has been an earthquake in the city. You are stuck in the hotel, which might have some secrets… Once all of them are found, they can lead you to the exit. The hotel will collapse in an hour. Will you make it out in time?
